lead_paragraph: Damian Lillard scored 39 points and the Portland Trail Blazers extended their winning streak in home openers to a league-record 16 straight games with a 113-104 victory over the Utah Jazz on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Lillard Scores 39, Blazers Run Home-Opening Win Streak to 16
